  <summary date="2024-02-27T20:54:35Z" status="Introduced in House">Military Food Security Act of 2023

This bill modifies how gross household income is calculated for purposes of determining a servicemember's eligibility for a basic needs allowance (i.e., a supplemental monthly payment for basic needs) from the military department concerned. Under the bill, gross household income is calculated by subtracting the basic housing allowance paid to any servicemember from their household income.</summary>
